<p><strong><em>长夜漫漫，唯有孤灯闪烁于舞台之上</em></strong></p>
<div class="list-pages-box">    

<p><strong><tt>1</tt></strong>. <strong><a href="/a-story-of-the-fire">剧目-火的故事</a></strong> <strong><tt>[+108 (+123/-15)]</tt></strong><br />
